If you don't try you don't know! Cheers ?
“I went to brush something off my cheek, and it was the floor”-Raymond Chandler / Drinking mosty WC brews in NYC
Lover of bone-dry Lambics, roasty (coffee) Stouts, fruity Sours, unfiltered Lagers and all kinds of IPA.

items.checkin_comment: Quite lively on opening although large CO2 bubbles. Certain tin tough to hop aroma and taste. Backend all grassy earthy hops. Just that tin in the front and on nose lets it down. Ok but there are better.
